'From Cuis 3.0 of 18 January 2011 [latest update: #768] on 2 March 2011 at 6:03:53 pm'!!CodeProvider methodsFor: 'diffs' stamp: 'jmv 3/2/2011 18:01'!wordDiffButton	"Return a checkbox that lets the user decide whether regular diffs should be shown or not"	^ (PluggableButtonMorph		model: self		stateGetter: #showingWordDiffs		action: #toggleWordDiffing)			label: 'wordDiffs';			 setBalloonText: 'Show code differences from the previous version, word by word.'! !